{"tid":1437381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毋忘雨傘敗仗] 我們處於劣勢，不要被帶風向","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:21:21.000Z","uid":71037,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8604f36d0f303ca3cf5d44fc3972d38dc4d78ee6","tid":1437381,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">直至今日－<br />\n已有5 位義士身亡以身名志。<br />\n已有223 位手足被捕隨時被告暴動罪。<br />\n5 大訴求無一達成、官警鄉黑治港帶頭破壞法治。<br />\n中共對香港取態越趨強硬。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n小弟有以下意見想發表：<br />\n1. 開始越來越多人恥笑警犬日日4pm 記招，膠化事件。 <br />\n<br />\n2. 淺黃/深黃/和理/勇武/泛民開始互相指責。 (我認同不應有任何人騎劫運動做大台，因為會害死全香港人，但我地勸完就算，提高警剔、唔好比任何人做on9 野就得)。<br />\n  <br />\n3. 越來越多人放大個別事件細節 (e.g. 方仲賢之前被濫捕/福建幫/黑心店 etc., 係, 呢堆事係無法無天，係好多仆街，但呢d 事只會日日不停上演，唔迫到政權跪低只會有更多呢類痴線野, 同樣既post/指責不用千千萬萬次重覆轉移大家焦點。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更何況，要逐樣追究既話，追究一世都追唔完。</span><br />\n<br />\n建議: <span style=\"color: red;\">做public record 將所有事情記低</span>，留待勝利後再度審判。  我地而家最重要既目標唔係要報仇或者要睇住某d 人死 （係，我明大家望到好多人都好憤怒，keep 住團火但<span style=\"color: red;\">集中火力令政權跪低</span>啦好嗎? 我地未贏ga, 唔好被仇恨衝昏腦袋，我地最大既目標係要<span style=\"color: red;\">撥亂反正、還政於民</span>。）  <br />\n<br />\n4. 應集中火力做極多文宣比中立/淺藍/淺黃, 鞏固黃方勢力。<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣不足！</span>  <br />\n<br />\n5. 冷處理五毛三毛及深藍、就算嘈贏佢地都對成場運動無用。深藍病入膏肓無得救。何況、你叫既得利益者主動放棄自己的利益(權、榮華富貴，他們會願意嗎? 只有實際行動才有效)  <br />\n<br />\n6. 停止神化任何人，係要保障手足不要被推舉為「領袖」受打壓送頭、同時保持「無大台無領袖」運動優勢。  <br />\n<br />\n7. 應開始強烈宣揚<span style=\"color: red;\">本土文化</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">培養香港人歸屬感及自我身份認同、以香港為傲發自豪</span></strong></span>。<br />\n(例如廣東話、中港分別等等。) <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(去到今時今日，都仲有on9 鬼妹仔以為香港人係會食狗肉同貓肉的)  </span></span><br />\n<br />\n8. 不要太計較隊友手段，只要是能令終極大魔王頭痛的手段，我都會支持、最少能做到不反對不割蓆。  <br />\n<br />\n9. 集火要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「真雙普選」</span></span></strong>，做到呢樣先有資格話係「階段性勝利」。(雖然我真係好憎呢個term) (明白有人既目標係想獨立，但香港而家好多人都係好保守，應先拎到真雙普選、之後再作打算。)  <br />\n<br />\n10. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「香港人」</span></strong>已經昇華做一種<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">精神</span></strong>、並非種族、膚色所奠定。我們支持的是一種<span style=\"color: green;\">普世價值</span>。(真香港人例子: 利君雅、持中國護照但聲援香港人的中國人、旅居海外但心繫香港的華人、不是在香港出生的梁天琦，等等)  <br />\n<br />\n結語：團結就是力量。 我們是一體，不要再被動搖。 <br />\n不要再著眼於港共官員說的廢話和分化手段。 <br />\n不要再無限放大雞毛蒜皮的小事。(e.g. 藍衫9 衝被白衫喝止呢d 無聊笑料) <br />\n應用對策團結自己人，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再加強文宣</span></span></strong>。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們不散、這場戲才能唱下去。</span>  <br />\n<br />\n最後容許我肉麻講一句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我愛香港、我愛香港人。 <br />\n天祐香港。 </span>"},{"pid":"dc97f59d99b040819b70ee0ede4bf82b361d72d5","tid":1437381,"uid":71037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"真係要多d 著重於香港的文宣！"},{"pid":"f1072aeebea47c3b0214390d66a0eb8a39a34724","tid":1437381,"uid":303110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n我是香港人，不是中國人！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec205af4358169a42df34ab841f6095e4028ed7","tid":1437381,"uid":190928,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雨傘敗在左膠，講完</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"58b13650cca5a68473772a59f02c1f71a41eabdb","tid":1437381,"uid":21572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"非常同意第3點 721上環依家冇哂消息"},{"pid":"f17b98b9e0cf2161c00c1a7aab3cff49951721de","tid":1437381,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec205af4358169a42df34ab841f6095e4028ed7","tid":1437381,"uid":190928,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雨傘敗在左膠，講完</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"左膠係累事<br />\n但今次已經比2014 收斂好多"},{"pid":"bbac2eb51946616798bed9d07f6892e52dc3f9d0","tid":1437381,"uid":71037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58b13650cca5a68473772a59f02c1f71a41eabdb","tid":1437381,"uid":21572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"非常同意第3點 721上環依家冇哂消息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"但我都認為要有個public record 一路記住所有事情"},{"pid":"4edd81108aa530a71211d7386860d5ed8cd9839a","tid":1437381,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"其實6位啦"},{"pid":"b70fa33940e42871bcdbe36d5cab6963a978b725","tid":1437381,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff16a4da8d36c4d711c1369f823e61cc8d8892bd","tid":1437381,"uid":257422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭拒五大訴求，望社會「move on」搞經濟</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190809/59914326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F59914326&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=8869df85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F59914326&h=be2780ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190809/59914326</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9Tx6Ti.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9Tx6Ti.png&h=5eda3115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Well......</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8qAkdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8qAkdB.jpg&h=4075ce61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqmWO62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqmWO62.jpg&h=025d7584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExJBC9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExJBC9C.png&h=09b37a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Codx3B5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCodx3B5.jpg&h=90ddc2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/09/120301_b905b9b5650f3b34258a66f2e8b8fc2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F120301_b905b9b5650f3b34258a66f2e8b8fc2e.png&h=3d914307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">811繼續和你飛</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/09/120305_2fcb570771afe303bc6f3775b432a504.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2