 />\n最後容許我肉麻講一句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我愛香港、我愛香港人。 <br />\n天祐香港。 </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"日。五。罷買救港<br />\n<br />\n罷買運動正式開始<br />\n之前推過罷買,反應唔錯,於是同其他巴打一齊統一搞左星期五,日罷買, 一星期2日, 請幫手集中推以下2個POST<br />\n<br />\n(和理非全面升級)星期五，日0消費！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436038/page/1</a><br />\n「驚就唔好出街！」BYE BUY DAY 全城罷買投票結果出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436025/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436025/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"儲錢減消費的確係合情合法最和理非既手段"},{"pid":"cbaf79e19ceea36d5597e1171df14abe1afb61eb","tid":1437381,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"我知東方啲抽水好好睇<br />\n<br />\n但唔好唔記得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係輸緊 五大訴求 一個都無回應到</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"3c9343502d0d905f94648c02ae9861761473cec3","tid":1437381,"uid":157312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"[文宣組急入] 向中國大陸輸出革命文宣方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437447</a>"},{"pid":"ce9555d80d5b1b8d9a0cf3bf756d08f407802c00","tid":1437381,"uid":282693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"停，就輸！"},{"pid":"8e779d79a350912778d56d5cc4c7e7de7225a952","tid":1437381,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bfee28411a60e5c6eea4c76487923f9a0f5b39b","tid":1437381,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"totally agree！<br />\n港共三毛不停出手模糊焦點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"係，對家一直暗暗出招<br />\n香港人轉數快又鐘意新奇八卦野<br />\n結果好易被d gimmick/gossip news 搶fo<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"fo